OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHuman rights watchdog      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpublishes single-sex spaces
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fguide                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Services such as bathrooms and domestic
OL,6, abuse refuges can be single sex in     
OL,7, certain circumstances, Britain's human 
OL,8, rights body has said in new guidance.  
OL,10,FHowever, the guidance from the Equality
OL,11,Fand Human Rights Commission says such  
OL,12,Fservices should be open to trans people
OL,13,Fwherever possible.                     
OL,15,FExceptions are only acceptable if there
OL,16,Fare "proportionate and justified       
OL,17,Freasons".                              
OL,19,FThe new guidance is an interpretation  
OL,20,Fof existing equality laws.             
